{"tid":2300368,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★BitCoin 重上1.9萬，「女股神」：可見50萬美元！！！","createTime":"2020-11-25T12:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T23:38:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"6cd4ae60439fd753ca0a0f6027961647b98e2453","tid":2300368,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T12:46:21.000Z","msg":"比特幣價格氣勢如虹，昨日(24日)一度高見19,416.6美元，逼近2017年的19,497美元紀錄高點。今(25日)即市一度跌至18,555.8美元，最新重上1.9萬美元關口，現報19,160.72美元，升2.94%。投資界熱捧比特幣，被稱為<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">「女股神」</span></strong>的ARK Investment創辦人、對沖基金經紀Catherine Wood最牛，其近日發表的預測料<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>比特幣可見50萬美元</strong></span>！<br />\n<br />\n比特幣年初至今累計升幅1.6倍，除了避險因素外，今年5月比特幣減少了每個區塊獎勵的新幣數量，意味比特幣的「挖礦」產出減半，令供應減少而價格上升。<br />\n<br />\nARK Investment創辦人、對沖基金經紀Catherine Wood指出，機構一直在增加對比特幣的分配，這一趨勢就如同機構投資者首次進入房地產和新興市場時一樣，都是由開始到逐漸加倉，若有更多機構投資者買入比特幣，其價格有望升至40至50萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201125/bkn-20201125104534698-1125_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20201125%2Fbkn-20201125104534698-1125_00842_001.html&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwoGpPR2DWAUw81xbwDiv9SI%3D&h=c4f9a4ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201125/bkn-20201125104534698-1125_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3ac34acee1ca95bd3edab941cc079a6a03f56884","tid":2300368,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T12:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab718a169b4b8329f8b49b01d41bb612f07bde0","tid":2300368,"uid":269125,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"re